    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279830/extras/c3066811f04f0bdea4702e6c78c32365.avif?t=1758586710\" width=1560 height=467 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >     <strong>《导演，请多多指教》是steam全球首部导演模拟器，而您则将化身导演，经历从选角到发掘演员的内心的一系列内容，为拍摄出一部完美的作品而殚精竭虑。6位性格各异的女性，将会给您的电影生涯带来怎样的变化？</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关于游戏：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>「这是一个关于娱乐圈的故事」</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279830/extras/105212de177c4251991dab1eeff3d393.poster.avif?t=1758586710\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279830/extras/105212de177c4251991dab1eeff3d393.webm?t=1758586710\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279830/extras/105212de177c4251991dab1eeff3d393.mp4?t=1758586710\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>      </strong>励志打造影视行业模拟器类游戏，让您体验娱乐圈/影视行业最真实的过程。您将化身导演，从初识陌生环境、到发掘优秀的演员、再到行业内幕、走进演员内心。是陪伴多年的助理、性感知性的女投资人、还是风格迥异的女演员们；是去探索影视行业最纯净的一面，还是去体验娱乐圈的“潜规则”；都由您来选择，导演，请多多指教~</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279830/extras/fbef3004011d7f0517a29aa5cc91bb81.avif?t=1758586710\" width=1560 height=467 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >是天真烂漫的校园女神？</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>「杜雨纯」</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279830/extras/ef1238a5e9e7099b00dafead6b01f6b7.avif?t=1758586710\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279830/extras_big/ef1238a5e9e7099b00dafead6b01f6b7.avif?t=1758586710 width=800 height=458 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279830/extras/4c91b0f0b67f9cead816a52fa2910cb5.poster.avif?t=1758586710\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279830/extras/4c91b0f0b67f9cead816a52fa2910cb5.webm?t=1758586710\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279830/extras/4c91b0f0b67f9cead816a52fa2910cb5.mp4?t=1758586710\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >是活泼灵动的富家千金？</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>「林潇潇」</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279830/extras/8aba51633cb78769a2cfe37e328aae52.avif?t=1758586710\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279830/extras_big/8aba51633cb78769a2cfe37e328aae52.avif?t=1758586710 width=800 height=458 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279830/extras/d687531b948f508b49f4420af697e942.poster.avif?t=1758586710\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279830/extras/d687531b948f508b49f4420af697e942.webm?t=1758586710\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279830/extras/d687531b948f508b49f4420af697e942.mp4?t=1758586710\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >是温婉大方的知性美女？</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>「朱可可」</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279830/extras/b8a4b56a5bb456b626e4efa38e7c52e4.avif?t=1758586710\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279830/extras_big/b8a4b56a5bb456b626e4efa38e7c52e4.avif?t=1758586710 width=800 height=458 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279830/extras/ecd64f865865ff485dd2a8f1b418a866.poster.avif?t=1758586710\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279830/extras/ecd64f865865ff485dd2a8f1b418a866.webm?t=1758586710\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279830/extras/ecd64f865865ff485dd2a8f1b418a866.mp4?t=1758586710\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >是清纯可人的生活助理？</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>「乔七七」</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279830/extras/7b6778f66e2d3e5fd711bc676e3314a4.avif?t=1758586710\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279830/extras_big/7b6778f66e2d3e5fd711bc676e3314a4.avif?t=1758586710 width=800 height=458 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279830/extras/85bdc7226bba3edbf874ac1b7a341e97.poster.avif?t=1758586710\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279830/extras/85bdc7226bba3edbf874ac1b7a341e97.webm?t=1758586710\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279830/extras/85bdc7226bba3edbf874ac1b7a341e97.mp4?t=1758586710\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >是年少成名的当红女星？</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>「孙芊颂」</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279830/extras/c6677aa02a73225d9568ff6ee340f024.avif?t=1758586710\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279830/extras_big/c6677aa02a73225d9568ff6ee340f024.avif?t=1758586710 width=800 height=458 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279830/extras/ee656f974e3b1cb4d229209801a07bf3.poster.avif?t=1758586710\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279830/extras/ee656f974e3b1cb4d229209801a07bf3.webm?t=1758586710\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279830/extras/ee656f974e3b1cb4d229209801a07bf3.mp4?t=1758586710\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >是性感强势的行业精英？</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>「陈悦」</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279830/extras/9fc5061ede9b7c40896dd7283159445e.avif?t=1758586710\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279830/extras_big/9fc5061ede9b7c40896dd7283159445e.avif?t=1758586710 width=800 height=458 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279830/extras/c40871e34d494cda749bea07c22e9915.poster.avif?t=1758586710\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279830/extras/c40871e34d494cda749bea07c22e9915.webm?t=1758586710\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279830/extras/c40871e34d494cda749bea07c22e9915.mp4?t=1758586710\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >产品特色：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >·第一视角沉浸体验——全程第一视角沉浸式体验导演生活中的喜怒哀乐</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >·多支线内容体验——每位角色都将带来不同的剧情体验</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >·真人实景拍摄——全方位还原导演日常生活场景</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >·多位主角可攻略——六位风情各异的美女，与你发生的风月故事</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >·隐藏故事——等你发现</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279830/extras/337546908b0dd0404abb63dc41d784ca.poster.avif?t=1758586710\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279830/extras/337546908b0dd0404abb63dc41d784ca.webm?t=1758586710\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279830/extras/337546908b0dd0404abb63dc41d784ca.mp4?t=1758586710\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279830/extras/ec98670b4d59bad263bf8ddacc0195ac.avif?t=1758586710\" width=1560 height=230 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >       <i><strong>尊敬的各位导演（玩家），您好，经历了近一年的制作，从前期筹备，到拍摄，到后期。终于迎来了即将跟各位的见面。有意思的是，您即将会感受我们的整个流程，从前期选角，到二轮面试，到实地拍摄，再到后期制作。在这个内容频多的影视行业，我们可能仅仅呈现了一个小小的角落，但是我们希望用最真实的情感，跟方式，变成一个您了解影视行业的开始。我们希望这款游戏是开放式的，所以我们不会有任何限制。最简单的yes-no，变成了贯穿我们整个剧情的始终，我们希望选择是多种多样的。多支线的错综复杂，希望让您能选择自己最想要的一条路。选择影视行业这个题材，是来源于我们团队这些年经历的素材，希望给您塑造出一个真实的影视行业。最后，希望我们可以建立起沟通，我们的沟通方式如下。</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >QQ粉丝群：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >     导演，请多多指教 粉丝1群 群号：1055676793</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >     导演，请多多指教 粉丝2群 群号：659484134</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >     导演，请多多指教 粉丝3群 群号：1055675869</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >全网官方账号：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >     导演，请多多指教「微信公众号，抖音，小红书，微博，快手，小黑盒，taptap」</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>   （我们会在官方自媒体账号以及粉丝群发放亲笔签名照以及游戏周边产品）</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >商务联系邮箱：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >     <a href=\"mailto:daoyan@xingyuanxingyi.com\">daoyan@xingyuanxingyi.com</a></p>",
